The escapees were identified as Dingaan Mtshwene (35), who was arrested for rape and robbery with aggravating circumstances, Mahlatse David Sithole (32), who was arrested for rape and Vusi John Mabona (33), who was arrested for murder and rape. The escapees allegedly escaped when the police were doing their routine services in the cells. The police pursued the escapees and managed to re-arrest Mtshwene. According to Colonel Moatshe Ngoepe, the circumstances surrounding their escape are still being investigated.
The manhunt for the remaining two escapees is still underway. Anyone with information may contact Detective Warrant Officer Mhletshwa Shabangu on 082 303 9894, the Crime Stop number 086 001 0111 or their nearest police station. 